<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <title><%= content_for(:title) || "Sports News" %></title>
    
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <meta name="format-detection" content="telephone=no">
    <meta name="apple-mobile-web-app-capable" content="yes">
    
    <%= csrf_meta_tags %>
    <%= csp_meta_tag %>
    
    <%= yield :head %>

    <link rel="manifest" href="/manifest.json">
    <link rel="icon" href="/icon.png" type="image/png" sizes="32x32">
    <link rel="icon" href="/icon.svg" type="image/svg+xml">
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/icon.png">

    <!-- Google Ad Script --> 
    <script async src="https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-9420999689089460" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>
    
    <%= stylesheet_link_tag "application", "data-turbo-track": "reload" %>
    <%= javascript_importmap_tags %>
  </head>

  <body>
    <%= render 'layouts/navbar' %>
    <%= yield %>

    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/fetch/2.0.4/fetch.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js" integrity="sha384-DfXdz2htPH0lsSSs5nCTpuj/zy4C+OGpamoFVy38MVBnE+IbbVYUew+OrCXaRkfj" crossorigin="anonymous" defer></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/popper.js@1.16.1/dist/umd/popper.min.js" integrity="sha384-9/reFTGAW83EW2RDu2S0VKaIzap3H66lZH81PoYlFhbGU+6BZp6G7niu735Sk7lN" crossorigin="anonymous" defer></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.5.3/dist/js/bootstrap.min.js" integrity="sha384-w1Q4orYjBQndcko6MimVbzY0tgp4pWB4lZ7lr30WKz0vr/aWKhXdBNmNb5D92v7s" crossorigin="anonymous" defer></script>

    <footer style="font-size: 10px;">
      <p>All logos, images, trademarks, and other media displayed on this site are the property of their respective owners, including but not limited to the MLB, MLS, NBA, NFL, NHL, and ESPN. These assets are used under the fair use doctrine for the purpose of identifying teams, leagues, and players, as well as reporting news and sharing publicly available information. This site is not affiliated with, endorsed by, or officially licensed by any sports leagues, teams, or media entities. Highlight videos, standings, and news content are provided through external APIs, including ESPN and other authorized sources, and are displayed in accordance with their terms of service. It is the user's responsibility to ensure compliance with local intellectual property laws.</p>
    </footer>


  </body>
</html>
